      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite covering hemolysis model; formal software validation plan required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and regression tests exist for core fluid solver, but hemolysis sub-model lacks dedicated regression coverage. No formal software validation plan exists. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4."
