      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) or equivalent applied to hemolysis transport equations; order-of-accuracy confirmed.",
      "rationale": "MMS applied to Navier-Stokes equations only; hemolysis power-law transport equation not verified via MMS. Observed order of accuracy not confirmed for hemolysis QoI. Achieved level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
