      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, operating conditions, and fluid properties sufficiently similar to COU; formal similarity assessment documented.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump geometry used for validation differs from proprietary VAD geometry in blade count, tip clearance, and volute design. Operating speed range partially overlaps COU envelope. Formal similarity assessment not completed. Achieved level 2."
    },
