      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model selection justified with sensitivity analysis; alternative model forms evaluated.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected without sensitivity study. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen) used without evaluation of alternative models (e.g., strain-based, Lagrangian). Model form uncertainty unquantified. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
