      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ conducted only for inlet boundary conditions and viscosity. Hemolysis model coefficients (C, alpha, beta in power-law) treated as deterministic despite known literature variability. Input uncertainty underestimated. Flagged as epistemic gap."
